Tyrael bows his head. This warrior seemed good... very good.

Tyrael: We were planning an attack just prior to your arrival. You
will likely be very useful to us. This being said, let us all resume
this meeting. Kaiser, your opinion is welcome anytime you want to give
it to us. The goal here will be to kill the Predacons on the spot.
Already, I have sent Deathsteel as an infiltrator in their ranks. He
will make it easier for us to get them. I was planning to use everyone
here to rip them apart. Anyone wants to back up now?

Dreadplague shakes her head. She's more than ready for action.
